se></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 20, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ncx1686824523526.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ncx1686824523526.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ncx1686824523526.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jpl1665702606595\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"jpl1665702606595___result_285500\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the result of certain ProcScript commands and tree widget events.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"jpl1665702606595__topic_d88481e1_d88482e1_d88483e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jpl1665702606595__p_d88484e1_d88485e1_d88486e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$result</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jpl1665702606595__p_d88487e1_d88488e1_d88489e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$result</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jpl1665702606595__topic_d58912e1_d58913e1_d58914e1_d58915e1_d58916e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d777231e76\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jpl1665702606595__p_d88493e1_d88494e1_d88495e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$result</span> function is set by many ProcScript statements and by tree widget events. For the values <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$result</span> can contain, see the documentation for the individual ProcScript statements.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jpl1665702606595__topic_d58917e1_d58918e1_d58919e1_d58920e1_d58921e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d777231e91\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jpl1665702606595__p_d88499e1_d88500e1_d88501e1\">Use in Form, Report, and Service components.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jpl1665702606595__p_d88502e1_d88503e1_d88504e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$result</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var> is allowed in Form components, but not in self-contained Report and Service components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jpl1665702606595__topic_d58922e1_d58923e1_d58924e1_d58925e1_d58926e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d777231e112\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jpl1665702606595__p_d88508e1_d88509e1_d88510e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$result</span> receives the result of several ProcScript command and tree widget events. For example:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jpl1665702606595__li_d35411e1_d35412e1_d35413e1\">First column of the last selected occurrence when a <code class=\"ph codeph\">SELECT</code> statement is included in an <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sql</span> statement.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jpl1665702606595__li_d35414e1_d35415e1_d35416e1\">Status of comparison made with the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">compare</span> statement.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jpl1665702606595__li_d35417e1_d35418e1_d35419e1\">Status of actions performed with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$ude</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jpl1665702606595__p_d88511e1_d88512e1_d88513e1\">In the debugger, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$result</span> can be accessed directly or as variable <code class=\"ph codeph\">$101</code>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/etu1719376772254.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>= (compute)</a><p>Assigns the value of an expression to a field, variable, or function.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exh1665702554603.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>addmonths</a><p>Adds the specified number of months to the date, storing the result of the calculation in $result.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nov1665702568299.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>filebox</a><p>Displays a file selection box.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hha1720076228830.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>length (deprecated)</a><p>Return the number of characters in the specified string.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hbo1720163290270.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>print</a><p>Activate printing.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fvo1665702607150.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>sql</a><p>Pass a DML statement to the specified DBMS path.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/udd1665702579942.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Status</a><p>Determines whether the status data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence modification state. It can be set or inspected using $occstatus. Valid values are True or False (default).</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4218757\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4218757\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$result Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 20, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return the result of certain ProcScript commands and tree widget events. $result $result = Expression Return Values The $result function is set by many ProcScript statements and by tree widget events. For the values $result can contain, see the documentation for the individual ProcScript statements. Use Use in Form, Report, and Service components. $result = Expression is allowed in Form components, but not in self-contained Report and Service components. Description $result receives the result of several ProcScript command and tree widget events. For example: First column of the last selected occurrence when a SELECT statement is included in an sql statement. Status of comparison made with the compare statement. Status of actions performed with $ude In the debugger, $result can be accessed directly or as variable $101 . Related Links = (compute) Assigns the value of an expression to a field, variable, or function. addmonths Adds the specified number of months to the date, storing the result of the calculation in $result. filebox Displays a file selection box. length (deprecated) Return the number of characters in the specified string. print Activate printing. sql Pass a DML statement to the specified DBMS path. Status Determines whether the status data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence modification state. It can be set or inspected using $occstatus. Valid values are True or False (default). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}